The finickiness of it stinks. Eventually you hear something you might want to adjust and just call it done anyway because it's close enough. I'd take it over not finishing something but that part is always an annoying end to making each song. Do you ever have this? I wonder if the digital age is partially to blame, where you can adjust every little thing at any moment in any way
